66c5cb99-8d3e-4735-b5a6-4226d32e0c81.title: Armour salesman
66c5cb99-8d3e-4735-b5a6-4226d32e0c81.text: And to you. Can I help you?

options.text: I'd like to see what you sell.

9a0d3b50-049b-4881-a019-a6d66d31fb91.title: <player>
9a0d3b50-049b-4881-a019-a6d66d31fb91.text: I'd like to see what you sell.

4e76eb33-c5c1-4e2f-a8cb-914bda044bf6.title: Armour salesman
4e76eb33-c5c1-4e2f-a8cb-914bda044bf6.text: Indeed, cast your eyes on my wares, adventurer.

6c164fc4-bbda-4779-a028-4e98e3f2f604.title: Armour salesman
6c164fc4-bbda-4779-a028-4e98e3f2f604.text:
I am a supplier of leather armours and accessories. Ask
and I will tell you what I know.

48d3341b-1fbb-4769-96e5-e2f06fe49d5e.title: Armour salesman
48d3341b-1fbb-4769-96e5-e2f06fe49d5e.text: I have normal, studded and hard types.

9d02458e-70f6-4cf5-aa0a-d94d2943b368.title: Armour salesman
9d02458e-70f6-4cf5-aa0a-d94d2943b368.text:
Indeed, leather armour is excellent for archers. It's
supple and not very heavy.

9b2b12cf-13f2-495c-9b2c-281df2a5f63f.title: Armour salesman
9b2b12cf-13f2-495c-9b2c-281df2a5f63f.text:
Ah, now that's leather covered with studs. It's more
protective than ordinary leather.

b7cd5151-aab6-42b1-8706-a3b4b651c5c2.title: Armour salesman
b7cd5151-aab6-42b1-8706-a3b4b651c5c2.text:
Hard leather is specially treated using oils and drying
methods to create a hard-wearing armour.

9f35771d-778d-4126-8ee1-bebc0d62e827.title: Armour salesman
9f35771d-778d-4126-8ee1-bebc0d62e827.text:
Ah yes we have a new range of accessories in stock.
Essential items for an archer like you.

0f82c7a0-6839-4023-a81f-e713f457840e.title: Armour salesman
0f82c7a0-6839-4023-a81f-e713f457840e.text: We have vambraces, chaps, cowls and coifs.

fd7df1a6-e035-4e7e-b9c7-541238382874.title: Armour salesman
fd7df1a6-e035-4e7e-b9c7-541238382874.text:
Ah yes, vambraces. These useful items are for your
arms.

280a9aa2-1cf1-4624-9a8b-1b55da6149cd.title: Armour salesman
280a9aa2-1cf1-4624-9a8b-1b55da6149cd.text:
A protective sheath that favours the bow and arrow. An
essential purchase.

aa148e4d-3455-4edd-930e-5d3d29cb1307.title: Armour salesman
aa148e4d-3455-4edd-930e-5d3d29cb1307.text:
Chaps have two functions: firstly to protect your legs,
and secondly for ease of reloading arrows.

d800fdc7-29b9-44b8-8d0c-c96787f4be99.title: Armour salesman
d800fdc7-29b9-44b8-8d0c-c96787f4be99.text:
I can highly recommend these to you for quick
archery.

262d7fa2-4d75-47d1-9a9c-0d0b6d7f84b7.title: Armour salesman
262d7fa2-4d75-47d1-9a9c-0d0b6d7f84b7.text:
The cowl is a soft leather hat, ideal for protection with
maneuverability.

3442a8ee-faaa-4a82-9722-255511a3943a.title: Armour salesman
3442a8ee-faaa-4a82-9722-255511a3943a.text: These are highly favoured with our guards.

ae6d23a8-03f0-4285-80aa-cfd45efca73b.title: Armour salesman
ae6d23a8-03f0-4285-80aa-cfd45efca73b.text:
The coif is a specialized cowl, that has extra chain
protection to keep your neck and shoulders safe.

79cdf5cb-90bc-4f88-b437-96c8da14c9da.title: Armour salesman
79cdf5cb-90bc-4f88-b437-96c8da14c9da.text: An excellent addition to our range, traveller.
